==地理==
韋斯特沃德霍！因其衝浪海域和背靠草原的沙灘而聞名。韋斯特沃德霍！擁有兩個教堂，分別是韋斯特沃德霍！[[浸信会|浸信會教堂]]及[[三位一體|三位一體教堂]]。韋斯特沃德霍！的海岸是屬於北德文郡海岸的一部份。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thenorthdevonfocus.co.uk/westwardhopebbleridge.htm|title=Holding Back the Tide|publisher=North Devon Focus|accessdate=2013-04-22|archive-date=2013-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130820072902/http://www.thenorthdevonfocus.co.uk/westwardhopebbleridge.htm|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

[[A39公路|A39公路]]連接了韋斯特沃德霍！和[[巴恩斯特|巴恩斯特]]、比迪福德與[[布德|布德]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.atlantic-highway.co.uk/Special-Interest/Atlantic-Highway-Naming-History/Default.asp|title=The "Atlantic Highway" - Naming History|publisher=Atlantic Highway|accessdate=2009-04-03|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090324053258/http://www.atlantic-highway.co.uk/Special-Interest/Atlantic-Highway-Naming-History/Default.asp|archivedate=2009-03-24|deadurl=yes}}</ref>

==運動==
韋斯特沃德霍！的[[皇家北德文郡高爾夫俱樂部|皇家北德文郡高爾夫俱樂部]]成立於1864年<ref>[http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sponsored/travel/holiday-cottages/8201917/Golfing-holidays-in-the-West-Country.html Telegraph - Golfing holidays in the West Country] {{Wayback|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sponsored/travel/holiday-cottages/8201917/Golfing-holidays-in-the-West-Country.html |date=20130116072055 }} ''The Telegraph'', 15 December 2010, accessed 30 January 2012.</ref>，是[[英格蘭和威爾斯|英格蘭和威爾斯]]中最古老的[[高爾夫球場|高爾夫球場]]。<ref>Dowell, Phil, ''The English Golf Coast'', Melrose Books, 2006, ISBN 1-905226-43-8.</ref>除了高爾夫球場，韋斯特沃德霍！亦擁有一個卡丁車賽道和[[海濱浴場|海濱浴場]][[岩池_(韋斯特沃德霍！)|岩池]]。

